        an array containing the constants of this enum type, in the order they are declared

        public static Op valueOf​(String name)

        Parameters:
        name - the name of the enum constant to be returned.
        Returns:
        the enum constant with the specified name
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if this enum type has no constant with the specified name

      • forSymbol

        public static Op forSymbol​(String symbol)
        Get the Op corresponding to the given symbol. Note: some symbols correspond to multiple Ops:
        • For + or -, the binary operator is returned
        • For ++ or --, the post-increment operator is returned
        Parameters:
        symbol - symbol
        Returns:
        corresponding operator
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if no such Op exists
